lead_paragraph: When a flyover by a flock of pelicans briefly interrupted Novak Djokovic's final service game Sunday, he waved both arms and grinned as if he had just won a championship.

headline.print_headline: Djokovic Wins 6th Key Biscayne Title by Beating Nishikori
headline.main: Djokovic Wins 6th Key Biscayne Title by Beating Nishikori
